Complications and Mortality in Octogenarians Undergoing Lumbopelvic Fixation.

von Glinski A(1), Elia C(2), Ansari D(3), Yilmaz E(4), Takayanagi A(5), Norvell 
DC(6), Pierre CA(3), Abdul-Jabbar A(3), Chapman JR(7), Oskouian RJ(3).

